items.title: Trump Blasts 'Fake Polls From Fake News Organizations'
items.description: President Donald Trump has called out liberal media pollsters for pushing anti-Trump narratives aimed at tarnishing his legacy at the 100-day mark.

items.title: White House: Trump 'Active' in Tariff Negotiations
items.description: President Donald Trump "is now in active negotiations with many" countries subjected to his tariffs, according to a White House statement Monday.

items.title: Trump: Biden Admin Prosecutions 'Made Me Stronger'
items.description: President Donald Trump told The Atlantic that being prosecuted by the Biden administration's Justice Department "made me a lot stronger."
